 = Dmitrij | last2 = Zenkovsky | first2 = Serge A. | last3 = Porter | first3 = Richard E. | title = Comparative History of Slavic Literatures | date =  | publisher = Vanderbilt University Press | location =  | isbn = 0-8265-1371-9 | pages =  vi|quote="Two Greek brothers from Salonika, Constantine who later became a monk and took the name Cyril and Methodius.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book  | title = The illustrated guide to the Bible | url = https://archive.org/details/illustratedguide0000port_g8d4 | year = 1998 | publisher = Oxford University Press | location = New York  | isbn = 0-19-521462-5 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/illustratedguide0000port_g8d4/page/14 14]|quote=In Eastern Europe, the first translations of the Bible into the Slavoruic languages were made by the Greek missionaries Cyril and Methodius in the 860s }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book  | last1 = Smalley | first1 = William Allen | title = Translation as mission: Bible translation in the modern missionary movement | url = https://archive.org/details/translationasmis0000smal | year = 1991 | publisher = Mercer | location = Macon, Ga.  | isbn = 978-0-86554-389-8 | pages =[https://archive.org/details/translationasmis0000smal/page/25 25]|quote=The most important instance where translation and the beginning church did coincide closely was in Slavonic under the brothers Cyril, Methodius, with the Bible completed by A.D. 880 This was a missionary translation but unusual again (from a modern point of view) because not a translation into the dialect spoken where the missionaries were The brothers were Greeks who had been brought up in Macedonia,  }}</ref>。

860年，[[西里尔_(东罗马帝国传教士)|西里尔]]和美多德与受[[东罗马帝国|东罗马帝国]]皇帝[[米海尔三世|米海尔三世]]和[[君士坦丁堡牧首|君士坦丁堡牧首]][[佛提烏|佛提烏]]的命令去[[可萨汗国|可萨汗国]]阻止[[犹太教|犹太教]]的扩张。因为可萨人信奉犹太教可以免除一些政治纠纷，[[可萨汗国|可萨汗国]]可汗坚定地将[[犹太教|犹太教]]作为国教，所以这次任务失败了。

公元862年，[[大摩拉维亚|大摩拉维亚]]的君主[[罗斯季斯拉夫_(大摩拉维亚)|罗斯季斯拉夫]]要求[[东罗马帝国|东罗马帝国]]皇帝[[米海尔三世|米海尔三世]]和[[君士坦丁堡牧首|君士坦丁堡牧首]][[弗提乌一世|弗提乌一世]]派传教士给斯拉夫人传福音。[[米海尔三世|米海尔三世]]迅速选择了派[[西里尔_(东罗马帝国传教士)|西里尔]]与[[美多德|美多德]]去，并且说：“你们来自[[萨洛尼卡|萨洛尼卡]]，所有的[[萨洛尼卡|萨洛尼卡]]人都讲着纯正的斯拉夫语<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.utexas.edu/cola/centers/lrc/eieol/ocsol-3-X.html |title= Old Church Slavonic Online Lesson 3 |author= Todd B. Krause |coauthors= Jonathan Slocum |publisher= Linguistics Research Center at UT Austin |access-date= 2014-12-21 |archive-date= 2010-10-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101002040446/http://www.utexas.edu/cola/centers/lrc/eieol/ocsol-3-X.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>”公元863年，[[西里尔_(东罗马帝国传教士)|西里尔]]与[[美多德|美多德]]对[[大摩拉维亚|大摩拉维亚]]和[[潘诺尼亚|潘诺尼亚]]的[[斯拉夫人|斯拉夫人]]进行过传教活动。为了向斯拉夫人传教，他们利用希腊字母和一些自创的字母创造了[[格拉哥里字母|格拉哥里字母]]。[[格拉哥里字母|格拉哥里字母]]是第一种用来记录[[古教会斯拉夫语|古教会斯拉夫语]]的字母<ref>Liturgy of the Hours, Volume III, 14 February.</ref>。随后他们将[[圣经|圣经]]翻译成[[古教会斯拉夫语|古教会斯拉夫语]]，并在摩拉维亚推广了它。

在867年，[[尼古拉一世_(教宗)|教皇尼古拉一世]]邀请[[西里尔_(东罗马帝国传教士)|西里尔]]与[[美多德_(东罗马帝国传教士)|美多德]]去[[罗马|罗马]]，869年2月14日，[[西里尔_(东罗马帝国传教士)|西里尔]]在罗马去世。870年，[[美多德|美多德]]返回摩拉维亚并在885年4月6日在那里去世。

两兄弟后来都被[[东正教会|东正教会]]授予“'''斯拉夫人的传教士'''”的头衔。1880年，天主教教皇[[利奥十三世|利奥十三世]]在[[天主教|天主教]]將他们的慶日加到天主教的禮儀曆中。1980年，天主教教宗[[若望·保祿二世|若望·保祿二世]]宣布他们与[[诺尔恰|诺尔恰]]的[[本笃|圣本笃]]同為欧洲的[[主保圣人|主保圣人]]<ref name="Egregiae Virtutis">{{cite web | title =Egregiae Virtutis | url =http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/apost_letters/documents/hf_jp-ii_apl_31121980_egregiae-virtutis_lt.html | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090104182217/http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/apost_letters/documents/hf_jp-ii_apl_31121980_egregiae-virtutis_lt.html | archivedate =2009-01-04 | access-date =2014-12-21 }} Apostolic letter of Pope John Paul II, 31 December 1980 {{la icon}}</ref>。

